{"tid":1995381,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美總統特朗普：中國處理疫症手段證北京會用盡辦法阻我連任","createTime":"2020-04-30T08:08:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T01:12:00.000Z","uid":70063,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"215a3bbc2da9a11862c221802938439af6330283","tid":1995381,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T08:08:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E7%96%AB%E7%97%87%E6%89%8B%E6%AE%B5%E8%AD%89%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E6%9C%83%E7%94%A8%E7%9B%A1%E8%BE%A6%E6%B3%95%E9%98%BB%E6%88%91%E9%80%A3%E4%BB%BB/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586%25E7%2596%25AB%25E7%2597%2587%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E8%25AD%2589%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%2594%25A8%25E7%259B%25A1%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2598%25BB%25E6%2588%2591%25E9%2580%25A3%25E4%25BB%25BB%2F&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZyIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=331ed81c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586%25E7%2596%25AB%25E7%2597%2587%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E8%25AD%2589%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%2594%25A8%25E7%259B%25A1%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2598%25BB%25E6%2588%2591%25E9%2580%25A3%25E4%25BB%25BB%2F&h=62bc2c79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E7%96%AB%E7%97%87%E6%89%8B%E6%AE%B5%E8%AD%89%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E6%9C%83%E7%94%A8%E7%9B%A1%E8%BE%A6%E6%B3%95%E9%98%BB%E6%88%91%E9%80%A3%E4%BB%BB/</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普表示，從中國處理新型肺炎的手段就證明北京「會無所不用其極（will do anything they can）」阻止他連任。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在白宮接受路透社訪問時說，對於新型肺炎疫症擴散全球，美國可以如何追究中國責任，特朗普說自己有很多選項，但又沒有說明是什麼。<br />\n<br />\n他說：「中國會無所不用其極令我敗選。」又指中國想他的對手，即民主黨總統候選人拜登入主白宮，這樣就可以紓緩貿易戰及其他議題的壓力。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普說，中國持續以公關宣傳製造自己是無辜的形象，又指他同國家主席習近平早前達成的貿易協議，被這場疫症打亂。報道又引述一匿名白宮高層人員說，特朗普同習近平於三月底通話，非正式地同意中美暫停罵戰（war of words），但現在應該已經失效了。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普曾因為中國輿論和外交部人員不斷指病毒源頭可能在美國，而連日稱新型冠狀病毒是「中國病毒」，其後傳出中美元首通話，承諾兩國會合作抗疫。不過到近日，雙方又再「打咀炮」，不過，特朗普始終未有直接批評習近平。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普又在訪問中透露，南韓已同意向美國支付更多錢，以換取加強美韓國防合作：「我們可以達成協議。他們想達成協議，已經同意支付很多錢。」&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n特朗普多次表示，要調查中國在新型肺炎全球大流行一事的責任，他在本周一（27日）說，中國原本是可以阻止大流行發生的，「我們相信是可以在源頭上阻截的，原本是可以很快阻斷，那就不會擴散到全球。」「美國正嚴肅跟進調查 ⋯&nbsp;我們對中國不滿。」又說很多方法可以令中國承擔責任。"},{"pid":"501de42fb2f43c0894805ff47a22d4b04edab906","tid":1995381,"uid":270889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T08:10:01.000Z","msg":"EXCLUSIVE: Analysis Reveals China&rsquo;s Bot Army Waging Digital War on Trump<br />\n<a href=\"https://thenationalpulse.com/politics/chinas-bot-army-wages-digital-war-on-trump/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthenationalpulse.com%2Fpolitics%2Fchinas-bot-army-wages-digital-war-on-trump%2F&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZyIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=19bd093a\" target=\"_blank\">https://thenationalpulse.com/politics/chinas-bot-army-wages-digital-war-on-trump/</a>"},{"pid":"75f273ef2e38e931fd5c643b3c7b10f36030aa6f","tid":1995381,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T08:22:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e7f0a05dec7298f282c155bbe6c400a25812a6a","tid":1995381,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T08:43:03.000Z","msg":"上個月先話believe Xi can handle it very well<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3689c18b0e1650778d5121009114de21e90b1f9","tid":1995381,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T01:12:00.000Z","msg":"Xi, My friend ~"}]}